<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>丐帮集团™ · 官方网站</title>

<link rel="icon" href="music.jpg">

<style>
* {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
    font-family: "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
    background: #0d1117;
    color: #c9d1d9;
}

/* 顶栏 */
header {
    background: #161b22;
    padding: 15px 30px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #30363d;
}

.logo {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #58a6ff;
}

.nav a {
    margin-left: 20px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #c9d1d9;
}

.nav a:hover {
    color: #58a6ff;
}

/* 主区 */
.hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 80px 20px;
}

.hero h1 {
    font-size: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.hero p {
    opacity: 0.7;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
}

.btn {
    padding: 10px 20px;
    background: #238636;
    color: white;
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none;
    margin: 5px;
}

.btn:hover {
    background: #2ea043;
}

/* 项目区 */
.section {
    padding: 40px 60px;
}

.section h2 {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    border-left: 4px solid #58a6ff;
    padding-left: 10px;
}

.repo-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
}

.repo {
    background: #161b22;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: 1px solid #30363d;
    transition: 0.2s;
}

.repo:hover {
    border-color: #58a6ff;
    transform: translateY(-4px);
}

.repo h3 {
    color: #58a6ff;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.repo p {
    font-size: 14px;
    opacity: 0.7;
}

/* 底部 */
.footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px;
    border-top: 1px solid #30363d;
    opacity: 0.6;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
    <div class="logo">丐帮集团™</div>
    <div class="nav">
        <a href="#">首页</a>
        <a href="#projects">项目</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/Beggars-Group">GitHub</a>
    </div>
</header>

<div class="hero">
    <h1>丐帮集团 · Beggars Group</h1>
    <p>技术 · 游戏 · 自动化 · AI研究体系</p>

    <a class="btn" href="https://github.com/Beggars-Group">查看组织</a>
</div>

<div class="section" id="projects">
    <h2>核心项目</h2>

    <div class="repo-grid">

        <div class="repo">
            <h3>物理版象棋</h3>
            <p>融合物理机制与策略系统的创新象棋玩法。</p>
        </div>

        <div class="repo">
            <h3>绩律·天衡</h3>
            <p>数据计算与规则评估系统（原 yhs 项目）。</p>
        </div>

        <div class="repo">
            <h3>乞分君</h3>
            <p>Excel自动计分与记录工具。</p>
        </div>

        <div class="repo">
            <h3>MusicAutoPlayer</h3>
            <p>自动音乐播放与数据展示系统。</p>
        </div>

        <div class="repo">
            <h3>丐点名</h3>
            <p>启动器 + 点名系统 UI 框架。</p>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>

<div class="section">
    <h2>组织结构</h2>
    <p>
        丐帮集团第一院 · 物理版象棋开发与研究院<br>
        权限体系：NT（最高权限） / SSS（次高级权限）<br>
        AI体系：Zero 系列（星睿-Cortex / 晴光-Synapse 等）
    </p>
</div>

<div class="footer">
    © 2019 - <span id="year"></span> 丐帮集团™
</div>

<script>
    document.getElementById("year").textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
</script>

</body>
</html>
